comments: Embiid (PHI) has his arm slightly extended when marginal contact occurs with Rozier (MIA) during the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball and as he defends Embiid (PHI).
Lowry (PHI) grabs and holds Butler's (MIA) arm and initiates illegal contact that affects his ability to secure the pass.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) brings his off-arm toward Butler (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as Oubre Jr. releases away without applying force during the driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up in a screening position in Lowry's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Butler (MIA) has his arm slightly extended when marginal contact occurs with Lowry (PHI) during the drive.
Embiid (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball as he attempts to dislodges it away from Butler (MIA) prior to incidental arm contact occurring at the end of the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Martin (PHI) legally contests Rozier's (MIA) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with his slightly extended right leg.

Incidental leg contact occurs as Lowry (PHI) establishes a legal guarding position in Rozier's (MIA) path and makes clean contact with the ball prior to any incidental arm contact occurring with Rozier at the end of the drive.
Highsmith (MIA) and Lowry (PHI) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Martin (MIA) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Highsmith (MIA) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
